*rĭp, /rɪp/, /<tt>rIp</tt>/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-ɪp|Rhymes: -ɪp]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[tear]] in paper etc.
# A type of [[tide]] or current.
# (slang) A comical, embarrassing, or hypocritical event or action. 
