===Verb===
{{en-verb||p}}

# To cause something, usually paper, to rapidly become two parts.
# {{italbrac|woodworking}} To cut wood along (parallel to) the grain.  Contrast [[cross-cut]].
# {{cattag|slang|internet}} To copy data from optical disks such as cd's and dvd's to a hard drive.

